517
00:27:24,017 --> 00:27:26,061
after what happened
in court today.

518
00:27:26,103 --> 00:27:28,772
'We have friends
up in Iron Heights.'

519
00:27:28,814 --> 00:27:31,150
Prison can be a dangerous place.

520
00:27:34,778 --> 00:27:36,238
We're not done yet.

521
00:27:37,281 --> 00:27:40,033
I'm an attorney. Trust me.

522
00:27:40,075 --> 00:27:41,201
We're done.

523
00:27:42,911 --> 00:27:45,289
What do you need
to free Peter Declan?

524
00:27:45,331 --> 00:27:47,333
At this point

525
00:27:47,374 --> 00:27:50,002
nothing short of a signed
confession from Brodeur.

526
00:27:51,587 --> 00:27:54,131
- Where are you going?
- To get a confession.

527
00:27:55,591 --> 00:27:58,885
The company Mrs. Queen,
or Steele.

528
00:27:58,927 --> 00:28:01,679
Mrs. Queen-Steele.
She hyphenate?

529
00:28:01,721 --> 00:28:03,932
She seems like a woman
who would hyphenate.

530
00:28:03,974 --> 00:28:06,059
[clears throat]

531
00:28:06,101 --> 00:28:09,229
Right, the company she invested
in doesn't exist.

532
00:28:09,271 --> 00:28:11,607
- I don't understand.
- There was no investment.

533
00:28:11,649 --> 00:28:14,901
The money was used to set up
an offshore LLC called Tempest.

534
00:28:14,943 --> 00:28:16,278
I don't recall
that name being under

535
00:28:16,320 --> 00:28:17,737
the Queen Consolidated banner.

536
00:28:17,779 --> 00:28:19,281
'Cause it's not,
there's nothing registered

