744
00:40:42,023 --> 00:40:44,776
- What the hell's going on?
- Oliver, what's happening?

745
00:40:44,817 --> 00:40:46,945
You're under arrest on suspicion
of obstruction of justice.

746
00:40:46,986 --> 00:40:48,947
- Aggravated assault...
- Walter, stop them!

747
00:40:48,988 --> 00:40:51,324
Trespassing,
acting as a vigilante..

748
00:40:51,366 --> 00:40:52,909
Are you out of your mind?

749
00:40:52,951 --> 00:40:54,493
...and murder.

750
00:40:54,535 --> 00:40:56,246
You have the right
to remain silent.

751
00:40:56,288 --> 00:40:57,830
'If you give up that right..'

